# Rush 3D Game - Project Structure

## Overview
A professional 3D endless runner game inspired by Ketchapp's Rush, built with Three.js, JavaScript, and modern web technologies.

## Project Structure (50+ files)

```
rush-3d-game/
│
├── index.html
├── README.md
├── package.json
├── .gitignore
├── LICENSE
