## Key Features

### 1. Core Gameplay
- Endless runner mechanics
- Smooth camera following
- Physics-based movement
- Collision detection
- Score tracking

### 2. Visual Effects
- Particle systems
- Trail effects
- Color transitions
- Screen shake
- Post-processing

### 3. Game Systems
- Level generation
- Difficulty scaling
- Power-up system
- Achievement system
- Save/Load functionality

### 4. UI Components
- Main menu
- In-game HUD
- Pause menu
- Game over screen
- Settings panel

## Technology Stack

- **Three.js**: 3D rendering
- **JavaScript ES6+**: Core logic
- **HTML5 Canvas**: Rendering
- **Web Audio API**: Sound effects
- **LocalStorage**: Save data
- **CSS3**: UI styling

## Next Steps

1. Set up base files (package.json, index.html)
2. Create core game loop and scene
3. Implement player controller
4. Build level generation system
5. Add collision detection
6. Create UI components
7. Implement visual effects
8. Add audio system
9. Polish and optimize

